# Email        : rick.romig@gmail.com | rick.romig@mymetronet.com
# Created      : 12 May 2021
# Updated      : 12 Dec 2025
# Comments     : Cinnamon keybindings backup file stored in ~/.config
#              : Tested with Cinnamon DE on Mint 19+, LMDE 5+, Debian 10+
